# Element Plus Pro Components

Vue 3 + Element Plus port of [element-ui-pro-components](https://github.com/gameorstudy/element-ui-pro-components), inspired by Ant Design Pro Components. Provides schema-driven high-level components for forms and tables.

## Tech Stack

- Vue 3 (Composition API), TypeScript, Vite
- Element Plus + `@element-plus/icons-vue`
- Less for scoped component styles
- Vue JSX/TSX for render functions (Submitter, CustomRender, demos)

## Package Layout

```
packages/
  components/   # ProTable, ProForm, DialogForm, EditableProTable
  base/         # ProFormItem, CustomRender
  composables/  # Shared hooks (useOptions, useFieldValue)
  types/        # Shared interfaces (ProFormItemProps, RenderActions)
  utils/        # form, debounce, breakpoints
src/            # Dev playground only — not published API
```

## Import Alias

Always import internal modules via the package alias:

```ts
import ProFormItem from 'element-plus-pro-components/packages/base/pro-form-item'
import { useOptions } from 'element-plus-pro-components/packages/composables/useOptions'
```

Configured in `vite.config.ts` and `tsconfig.app.json` paths.

