## Migration Notes (Vue 2 → Vue 3)

- Preserve API parity with element-ui-pro-components where possible
- Replace Element UI types/props with Element Plus equivalents
- Use Vue 3 native `Fragment` instead of `vue-fragment`
- No `el-table-prepend` dependency needed
- Prefer `<script setup>` for new components; legacy `defineComponent` is acceptable in existing code
